This was a fairly quick remake of a map I made a long time ago called fy_poopynoncense
It is a cut in half version of cbble where you can go on the roof tops and battle it out.
I put new trees in to make it looks nice, and while the lighting isn't anything special its the same
as cbble's. I made ladder placement much more team balanced in this one. Its a fun map so i hope you enjoy it!!!
